that provides assistance and

00:03:17.440 --> 00:03:20.514
maintenance for both our own vessels
and those of our competitors.

00:03:20.687 --> 00:03:24.014
So I've travelled the world doing
small maintenance jobs on our boats.

00:03:27.186 --> 00:03:30.243
Seeing the ship finally in the
water is always satisfying.

00:03:48.799 --> 00:03:53.183
As a tradesman, it's important to choose a
career you're going to enjoy for a long time.

00:03:53.597 --> 00:03:57.851
It inspires you to do your best and then you
can move on to bigger and better projects.

